The Roman Catholic Church in Haiti comprises two ecclesiastical provinces, each headed by an archbishop. The province is in turn subdivided into 7 dioceses and 2 archdioceses, each headed by a bishop or an archbishop.
==List of Dioceses==
=== Ecclesiastical province of Cap-Haïtien===
* Archdiocese of Cap-Haïtien
** Diocese of Fort-Liberté
** Diocese of Hinche
** Diocese of Les Gonaïves
** Diocese of Port-de-Paix
===Ecclesiastical province of Port-au-Prince===
* Archdiocese of Port-au-Prince
** Diocese of Anse-à-Veau and Miragoâne
** Diocese of Jacmel
** Diocese of Jérémie
** Diocese of Les Cayes
